18/06/2021 - Discusses with Jay, Kamal and Delhi

1. URL always should be small letters. User hyphen to separate 
2. Should use provided API request methods as per standards. (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
3. Controller name can be singular or pulural as per requirements.

Example URLS:
Get list [GET]: https://api.domain.com/api/employees
Get Single [GET]: https://api.domain.com/api/employees/1
Create new [POST]: https://api.domain.com/api/employees
Update [PUT]: https://api.domain.com/api/employees/1
Delete [DELETE] :https://api.domain.com/api/employees/1
Additional methods : https://api.domain.com/api/employees/update-image/1
